Date of Birth: November 9, 1818<br/>
Birthplace: Saint Johnsbury, Vermont, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: February 12, 1849<br/>
Death: May 27, 1888<br/>
<br/>
Born Nov. 9, 1818, at Saint Johnsbury, Caledonia Co., Vermont, to Levi Snow and Lucina Streeter. Ordained apostle Feb. 12, 1849, by Brigham Young, at age 30; died May 27, 1888, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 69.